## What This Teaching Provides

When adopting teachings on the **framework spoke** specifically:

- **Project scope** = `templates/commands/` and other project files
- **WAI-Spoke/** = session infrastructure — never modified as part of project development
- Teaching adoption on the framework spoke is a **verification pass**, not an apply pass
- If the change is already in `templates/commands/`, move teaching to processed without edits
- The framework is always ahead of its own teachings — it generates them, then distributes downstream

